snippet.title: Celbugs: Coming soon to Steam!
snippet.description:
Soon, Celbugs will crawl onto Steam. There's some final polishing and finishing touches I need to work on, but watch this space for more info. Official release date should come within the next few weeks.

Celbugs is a colour-matching puzzle game in which you breed cute critters - Celbugs - and use them to beat levels.

Wishlist Celbugs on Steam now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2571330/Celbugs/
